    "Management": {
      "text": "Inflammatory complications\nMethylprednisolone\n1-2mg/kg in most cases\nInfectious\nStress dose\nsteroids\nwith\nhydrocortisone\n100mg IV Q8hr if on or recently on steroids\nDermatologic\nHydrocortisone\n1% cream\nIf drug induced lupus, stop medication and consider alternative",
